{"tid":1038423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男：醫生，我個鼻有無事？ 醫生：有牙！","createTime":"2019-02-26T16:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T12:05:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d377d8a1aa8d6170b4fd3dedcd1cbf5ee3fac264","tid":1038423,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"男：醫生，我個鼻有無事？<br />\n醫生：有牙！<br />\n男：牙你老母！<br />\n醫生：唔係呀！真係有牙&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n【罕見病例】丹麥男子鼻塞2年 原來鼻腔內生咗隻牙<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190224/large/1550952218_6137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190224%2Flarge%2F1550952218_6137.jpg&h=6f0bd232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n丹麥一名59歲男子鼻塞了2年，更失去嗅覺，他到醫院檢查，醫生發現他的鼻孔內有異物，於是做手術取出，發覺竟然是一隻牙齒。<br />\n<br />\n這宗病例刊登在醫學期刊《BMJ Case Reports》，負責的醫生富格桑（Milos Fuglsang）稱，病人患了罕見的鼻腔牙（intranasal retained tooth），自1959年到2008年只曾出現23宗病例。<br />\n<br />\n患者在過去兩年一直鼻塞，而且失去嗅覺，左邊的鼻孔更時常流出乳白色分泌物。他曾自行買類固醇噴霧，希望可紓緩病情，但不見成效，於是前往奧胡斯（Aarhus）大學醫院的耳鼻喉科檢查。<br />\n<br />\n醫生替他檢查鼻子後，發現鼻子彎曲到一邊，鼻腔內更有腫塊，最初懷疑是囊腫或腫瘤，因此決定動手術將異物取出，結果發現竟然是一隻牙齒。<br />\n<br />\n鼻腔牙以往的病例顯示，通常由於臉部受傷、感染或顎裂導致牙齒移位，但暫時都未能解釋成因。而這名患者年輕時下顎及鼻子曾經折斷，進行了重建手術，醫生們不能斷定兩者是否有關連，「牙齒可能早已存在患者的鼻孔內，只是最近才出現徵狀。」<br />\n<br />\n病人接受鼻腔鹽水沖洗及服用10天抗生素後，一個月內便告康復。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GJYekg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GJYekg&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6TKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=0d05455e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GJYekg</a>"},{"pid":"b15b17e3e7be0e97801fd29dc70358e0fd5881d1","tid":1038423,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"吾系甘牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c312da1801066fcf5a7823f03ad7321f3ef246","tid":1038423,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"牙牙牙牙"},{"pid":"0d4d284d3ff019dcdd07d88b8fd5e6f7dbe28f90","tid":1038423,"uid":59746,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"牙你老母"},{"pid":"03388316cd1f1363a49c71aac2db731f02fc31b3","tid":1038423,"uid":35221,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yams.akamaized.net/Assets/21/626/l_p1011662621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyams.akamaized.net%2FAssets%2F21%2F626%2Fl_p1011662621.jpg&h=73a642f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efc788dc9fa6b3a79fae980bdaa2e162e165e4a3","tid":1038423,"uid":41411,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"係香港 醫生開刀後見到有隻牙會縫返個位 然後轉介佢去其他專科"},{"pid":"ac713ccc2f566720796b8440f8dd95e722b9d75a","tid":1038423,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"03388316cd1f1363a49c71aac2db731f02fc31b3","tid":1038423,"uid":35221,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://yams.akamaized.net/Assets/21/626/l_p1011662621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyams.akamaized.net%2FAssets%2F21%2F626%2Fl_p1011662621.jpg&h=73a642f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f620b0d295e2472297942cc901a62c1bed2a471","tid":1038423,"uid":108090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"重諗住入黎牙你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23cd89c71f993e7563a2dd3cc804762b99ff7de","tid":1038423,"uid":68369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efc788dc9fa6b3a79fae980bdaa2e162e165e4a3","tid":1038423,"uid":41411,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"